<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Soru Cevap Portalı</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f2f4f7;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #5a67d8;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

            .navbar-brand:hover {
                color: #e2e8f0;
            }

        .container {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header-content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header-description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .btn {
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #5a67d8;
            border: none;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #434190;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            border-color: #a0aec0;
            color: #a0aec0;
        }

            .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
                background-color: #a0aec0;
                color: #fff;
            }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .feature {
            max-width: 200px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #edf2f7;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
        }

            .feature:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                background-color: #e2e8f0;
            }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #5a67d8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-description {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #718096;
        }

        .feature-btn {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #5a67d8;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

            .feature-btn:hover {
                background-color: #434190;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="header-title">Soru Cevap Portalı</div>
            <div class="header-description">Sorularınızı sorun, cevaplarınızı paylaşın ve topluluğumuzla etkileşime geçin.</div>
            <div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Başlayın</button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Daha Fazla Bilgi</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="features mt-5">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">Soru Sor</div>
                <div class="feature-description">Sorularınızı topluluğa sorarak hızlı ve doğru yanıtlar alın.</div>
                <a href="#" class="feature-btn">Soru Sor</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">Cevap Ver</div>
                <div class="feature-description">Bilginizi paylaşarak diğer kullanıcılara yardımcı olun.</div>
                <a href="#" class="feature-btn">Cevap Ver</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-title">Kategori Oluştur</div>
                <div class="feature-description">Ortak ilgi alanlarına sahip kullanıcılarla topluluk oluşturun.</div>
                <a href="" class="feature-btn">Kategori Oluştur</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
